  1964вҶ’### 4.4.3 PM Schedule Management Service
  1965вҶ’
  1966вҶ’Handles manual PM modifications (drag-and-drop, manual reschedules) with full validation including Maximo status locks.
  1967вҶ’
  1968вҶ’```typescript
  1969вҶ’/**
  1970вҶ’ * Service for manual PM schedule modifications.
  1971вҶ’ * 
  1972вҶ’ * CRITICAL: All modifications MUST validate against Maximo status to prevent
  1973вҶ’ * race conditions with in-progress work orders. The PMEditValidator from the
  1974вҶ’ * Integration layer (Part 7) provides this validation.
  1975вҶ’ * 
  1976вҶ’ * Operational reality (Maximo) MUST override planning data (MMS).
  1977вҶ’ */
  1978вҶ’class PMScheduleManagementService {
  1979вҶ’  private pmEditValidator: PMEditValidator;  // From Part 7
  1980вҶ’  private auditLogger: AuditLogger;
  1981вҶ’  
  1982вҶ’  /**
