  1984вҶ’   * 
  1985вҶ’   * @throws MaximoLockError if PM is in-progress in Maximo
  1986вҶ’   * @throws ComplianceWindowError if new date is outside allowed window
  1987вҶ’   * @throws TrackConflictError if track is occupied on new date
